Trading Bot Summary:

Type: Python bot (single file) using ccxt, pandas, and numpy.

Strategy: Moving Average Crossover (fast SMA vs. slow SMA).

Entry: Buys when fast SMA crosses above slow SMA.

Exit:

Takes profit at +1.5%

Stops loss at −1%

Also exits if strategy gives a sell signal.

Modes:

Simulation (paper trading) — default, no money risked.

Live mode — works with Binance or other ccxt exchanges.

Features:

Auto entry/exit logic

Take-profit & stop-loss

Position sizing by % of balance

Logging and cooldown between trades
